      "content": "i get that but my doctor is super busy and it's gonna take weeks to get an appointment. i'm already feeling terrible. if i just take a smaller dose of the zoloft for a few days while i start the st john's wort, is that okay? i just want to get off the chemicals as fast as possible.",
